Rating: 3
I have made cauliflower this way but with out preparing the sauce with the half and half. ( less calories ). Once the cauliflower has been steamed, I put the head in a shallow baking dish. Sprinkle with italian breadcrumbs then lay american cheese slices over the top to cover. I then sprinkle more italian breadcrumbs on the cheese slices. Bake in a preheated 350 degree oven for 5-10 minutes.